# Ansible-Vault

```bash
ansible-vault encrypt foo.yml bar.yml baz.yml # encript
ansible-vault decrypt foo.yml bar.yml baz.yml # decrypt
      
ansible-playbook --ask-vault-pass site.yml                            # run a play and ask for vault pass
ansible-playbook site.yml --vault-password-file ~/.vault_pass.txt     # run a play and read vault pass from file
export ANSIBLE_VAULT_PASSWORD_FILE=~/.vault_pass.txt                  # set env with filename to read vault pass from
```
    
